\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-55004a6 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"55004a6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cfd4572 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"cfd4572\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cc163ad elementor-widget elementor-widget-video\" data-id=\"cc163ad\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;youtube_url&quot;:&quot;https:\\\/\\\/youtu.be\\\/8Fj4Xtf5gO0&quot;,&quot;video_type&quot;:&quot;youtube&quot;,&quot;controls&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"video.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-wrapper elementor-open-inline\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-video\"><\/div>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-18288b8 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"18288b8\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-98db646 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"98db646\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Join <strong data-start=\"311\" data-end=\"327\">Kevin Joseph<\/strong>, Growth Marketing Head, and <strong data-start=\"356\" data-end=\"374\">Anbarasu Reddy<\/strong>, Head of Operations and General Manager, as they unpack the transformative impact of ERP data management on maintenance, procurement, and production processes.<\/p><p class=\"\" data-start=\"140\" data-end=\"521\">Enterprise systems are only as effective as the data behind them. Yet many companies invest heavily in ERP platforms while overlooking MRO data quality\u2014causing downtime, duplicate spend, and inefficiencies.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2398baf e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2398baf\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-acc6473 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"acc6473\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"987\" data-end=\"1013\"><strong data-start=\"991\" data-end=\"1013\">Overview:<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"140\" data-end=\"521\">Enterprise Resource Planning (ERP) systems are designed to streamline operations, improve visibility, and drive efficiency across departments. However, the true value of these systems depends entirely on the quality of the data they rely on\u2014particularly MRO (Maintenance, Repair, and Operations) data, which supports critical maintenance and production activities.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"523\" data-end=\"921\">Unfortunately, many organizations overlook this foundational layer. They pour resources into ERP implementations without addressing the underlying data inconsistencies\u2014resulting in inaccurate BOMs, unplanned downtime, inventory mismatches, and costly procurement errors. Inconsistent naming conventions, missing attributes, and free-text entries create chaos within otherwise sophisticated systems.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"923\" data-end=\"1156\">This episode explores why structured, standardized, and continuously governed MRO data is essential\u2014not just for accurate reporting, but for real-time decision-making, improved asset performance, and long-term operational resilience.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-10185dd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"10185dd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"949\" data-end=\"985\"><strong data-start=\"956\" data-end=\"985\">Key Discussion Highlights<\/strong><\/h3>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"987\" data-end=\"1197\"><strong data-start=\"987\" data-end=\"1038\">\ud83d\udd39How Poor Data Impacts Maintenance Operations<\/strong><br data-start=\"1038\" data-end=\"1041\" \/>Discover how inaccurate ERP-MRO data delays work orders, extends downtime, and increases technician workload\u2014and how structured data streamlines every step.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1199\" data-end=\"1381\"><strong data-start=\"1199\" data-end=\"1240\">\ud83d\udd39Procurement Without Maverick Spend<\/strong><br data-start=\"1240\" data-end=\"1243\" \/>Learn how standardized item descriptions and accurate specifications support smarter sourcing, better vendor negotiations, and compliance.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1383\" data-end=\"1571\"><strong data-start=\"1383\" data-end=\"1421\">\ud83d\udd39 Data-Driven Production Planning<\/strong><br data-start=\"1421\" data-end=\"1424\" \/>Understand how clean BoMs, accurate inventory visibility, and data consistency prevent stockouts and keep production running without interruptions.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1573\" data-end=\"1741\"><strong data-start=\"1573\" data-end=\"1615\">\ud83d\udd39Why One-Time Cleansing Isn\u2019t Enough<\/strong><br data-start=\"1615\" data-end=\"1618\" \/>Hear why traditional data cleansing doesn\u2019t last\u2014and why continuous data governance is essential for long-term ERP success.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1743\" data-end=\"1997\"><strong data-start=\"1743\" data-end=\"1785\">\ud83d\udd39Meet the AI Agents Behind the Magic<\/strong><br data-start=\"1785\" data-end=\"1788\" \/>From <strong data-start=\"1793\" data-end=\"1805\">AutoSpec<\/strong> and <strong data-start=\"1810\" data-end=\"1826\">AutoEnrichAI<\/strong> to <strong data-start=\"1830\" data-end=\"1843\">AutoClass<\/strong> and <strong data-start=\"1848\" data-end=\"1865\">AutoTranslate<\/strong>, discover how Verdantis&#8217; AI-powered agents automate data quality, classification, enrichment, and governance\u2014without manual effort.<\/p>\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"1999\" data-end=\"2218\"><strong data-start=\"1999\" data-end=\"2028\">\ud83d\udd39The Integrity Platform<\/strong><br data-start=\"2028\" data-end=\"2031\" \/>Get a closer look at <strong data-start=\"2052\" data-end=\"2075\">Verdantis Integrity<\/strong>, our real-time ERP data governance hub that connects to systems like SAP, Oracle, and Maximo to apply AI rules and policies organization-wide.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cda455d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cda455d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"\" data-start=\"2225\" data-end=\"2280\"><strong data-start=\"2231\" data-end=\"2280\">Takeaways for COOs, CIOs &amp; Operations Leaders<\/strong><\/h3>\n<ul data-start=\"2282\" data-end=\"2540\">\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2282\" data-end=\"2370\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2284\" data-end=\"2370\"><strong data-start=\"2284\" data-end=\"2319\">Treat data as a strategic asset<\/strong>\u2014assign owners, track KPIs, and maintain standards.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2371\" data-end=\"2459\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2373\" data-end=\"2459\"><strong data-start=\"2373\" data-end=\"2395\">Start with a pilot<\/strong>\u2014focus on a plant, a region, or a category to show results fast.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<li class=\"\" data-start=\"2460\" data-end=\"2540\">\n<p class=\"\" data-start=\"2462\" data-end=\"2540\"><strong data-start=\"2462\" data-end=\"2484\">Embrace automation<\/strong>\u2014AI-driven governance scales where manual efforts can\u2019t.<\/p>\n<\/li>\n<\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0d60456 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0d60456\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-185f934 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"185f934\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Meet The Speakers<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d3dcca5 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"d3dcca5\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6c43bfc e-con-full frosted e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"6c43bfc\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-04f9c83 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"04f9c83\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c88466 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5c88466\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a4e3edf elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a4e3edf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Anbarasu Reddy<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"